      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭子仪上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "壮怀磊落有谁知，一剑防身且自随。整顿乾坤济时了，那回方表是男儿。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "俺，姓郭名子仪，本贯华州郑县人也。学成韬略，腹满经纶，要思量做一个顶天立地的男儿，干一桩定国安邦的事业，今以武举出身，到京谒选，正值杨国忠窃弄威权，安禄山滥膺宠眷，把一个朝纲，看看弄得不成模样。想俺郭子仪，未得一官半职，不知何时，才能替朝廷出力也！",
      "text_length": 124
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "商调集贤宾",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "论男儿壮怀须自吐，肯空向杞天呼！笑他每似堂间处燕，有谁曾屋上瞻乌？不提防押虎樊熊，任纵横社鼠城狐。几回价听鸡鸣起身独夜舞。想古来多少乘除，显得个勋名垂宇宙，不争便姓字老樵渔！",
      "text_length": 87
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "旅寓无聊，且到长安市上买醉一回。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "逍遥乐",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "向天街徐步，暂遣牢骚，聊宽逆旅。俺则见来往纷如，闹昏昏似醉汉难扶，哪里有独醒行吟楚大夫？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "俺郭子仪呵！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "逍遥乐",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "待觅个同心伴侣，怅钓鱼人去，射虎人遥，屠狗人无！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭子仪下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "啊哈！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "酒保上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "我家酒铺十分高，罚誓无赊挂酒标。只要有钱凭你饮，无钱滴水也难消。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "小子是这长安市上，新丰馆大酒楼，一个小二哥的便是。我这酒楼，开在这东https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021272021-07-30西两市中间，往来十分热闹。凡是京城内外，王孙公子、官员仕户、军民百姓，没有一个不到我这酒楼上来喝这么三杯，也有吃寡酒的，吃案酒的，买酒去的，包酒来的，啊咦呀一天打发个不了。喂，伙计，把煤炉子通这么一通，伺候吃酒的来啊！",
      "text_length": 192
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "酒保下。郭子仪上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上京马",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "遥望见绿杨斜靠画楼隅，滴溜溜一片青帘风外舞，怎得个燕市酒人来共沽！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "酒家！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "来了，来了！爷是喝酒的么？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "楼上请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "待俺上楼去者！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "喂，伙计，有客上楼了！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "妙啊！好一座酒楼也！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上京马",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "敝轩窗日朗风疏，见四周遭粉壁上都画着醉仙图。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "爷，你是自饮，还是待客？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "独饮三杯，可有好酒？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "有好酒：金盘露、银盘露、梨花春、竹叶青、玉兰香、桑老白、绍兴老酒、高邮皮酒、山西汾酒、惠山麒酒、雪酒、药酒；还有两种……",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "哪两种？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "秀才瓮老婆醉。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "怎么有这个名儿？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "无非带点酸味儿。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "拣好酒取来。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "是了。喂，伙计，拿壶好酒用啊！爷，酒在此。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "斟。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "是了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "唔，唔，唔，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "好量啊。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "再斟。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "哎，我看爷也是爱喝这么一杯的。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "酒家。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "梧叶儿",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "俺非是爱酒的闲陶令，也不学使酒的莽灌夫，一谜价痛饮兴豪粗。撑着这醒眼儿谁偢保？问醉乡深可容得吾？听街市恁喧呼，偏冷漠高阳酒徒。",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二朝官同上，过场，同下。〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "酒家！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "哎，爷可是要添酒？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "我且问你，楼下那些官员都住何处去的？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "爷一面喝酒，待我告诉爷。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "讲。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "只为国舅爷杨丞相，并韩、虢、秦三位夫人，万岁爷各赐造新第。在这宣阳里中，四家府门相连，俱照大内一般样造法。这家造来要胜似那家，那家造来又要赛过这家，见那家造得华丽，这家便拆毁了，重新再造，定要与那家一样，https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021272021-07-30方才住手，一座厅堂，足足费了千万贯钱钞，今日才得完工。因此合朝大小官员，都备了羊酒礼物，前往那里去庆贺，打从这里经过，为此热闹。",
      "text_length": 215
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "哦，有这等事！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "哎，有这事。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "下去。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "待我再去拿酒来。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "酒保下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，想外戚宠盛到这个地位，如何是了也！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "醋葫芦怪私家恁僭窃，竞豪奢，夸土木。一班儿公卿甘作折腰趋，争向权门如市附。（白）再没一人呵！（醋葫芦）把舆情向九重公诉，可知他朱甍碧瓦总是血膏涂！",
      "text_length": 73
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭子仪吐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "唔！心中一时忿懑，不觉酒涌上来了，且向四壁间闲看一回。这壁上有细字数行，待我看来。（念）“燕市人皆去，函关马不归。若逢山下鬼，环上系罗衣。”（白）呀，这诗好生奇怪也！（幺篇）我这里定睛一直看，从头儿逐句读，细端详诗意少祯符。（白）且看是何人题的。“李遐周题。”这名儿好壬熟识啊。哦呵是了。我闻有个术士李遐周，能知过去未来，想必是他了。（幺篇）多则是就里难言藏谶语，猜诗谜杜家何处？早难道醉来墙上往笔乱鸦涂！",
      "text_length": 203
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "酒保上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "爷，您靠着窗户往下看。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖大开门〗。安禄山上，三笑，过场，下。〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "爷，您可曾看见那个大肚子的人么？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "这是何人？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "此人姓安名禄山。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭子仪"
      ],
      "text": "哦……呵！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902127",
      "scene_id": "70902127_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "酒保"
      ],
      "text": "郭子仪",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902127_e00066",
